OL,3,CPoverty strategy 'significant step
OL,4,Cforward' despite criticism, says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons has
OL,8,Finsisted a long-awaited Stormont plan
OL,9,F- 17 years in the making - to tackle
OL,10,Fpoverty will make a "meaningful
OL,11,Fdifference".
OL,13,FThat's despite the strategy been
OL,14,Fcriticised as "underwhelming" and it
OL,15,Flacking targets.
OL,17,FDUP MLA Lyons launched an extended 14-
OL,18,Fweek public consultation on the
OL,19,FExecutive's Anti-Poverty Strategy 2025-
OL,20,F35 on Tuesday.
