OL,3,CPoverty strategy 'significant step
OL,4,Cforward' despite criticism, says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FHe described it as being based on
OL,8,Fthree pillars of minimising risks of
OL,9,Ffalling into poverty, minimising the
OL,10,Fimpact of poverty on people's lives
OL,11,Fand working to help people get out of
OL,12,Fpoverty.
OL,14,FFigures indicated that around 18% of
OL,15,Fthose in Northern Ireland live in
OL,16,Frelative poverty, and 15% live in
OL,17,Fabsolute poverty, with 25% of children
OL,18,Fliving in relative poverty and 21% of
OL,19,Fchildren living in absolute poverty.
