OL,3,CPoverty strategy 'significant step
OL,4,Cforward' despite criticism, says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FThe strategic commitments from across
OL,8,Fdepartments include continuing the
OL,9,FExtended Schools Programme, working
OL,10,Fwith partners to scope out an NI Debt
OL,11,FRelief Scheme, a commitment to develop
OL,12,Fan Executive Disability Strategy and a
OL,13,FFuel Poverty Strategy.
OL,15,FSpeaking in the Assembly, Mr Lyons
OL,16,Fdescribed a "legacy of delay" in
OL,17,Ftaking forward an anti-poverty
OL,18,Fstrategy.
