OL,3,CPoverty strategy 'significant step
OL,4,Cforward' despite criticism, says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,F"When I took office, I made it clear
OL,8,Fthat one of my priorities would be
OL,9,Ftackling poverty," he told MLAs.
OL,11,F"After a legacy of delay in taking
OL,12,Fthis work forward, I wanted to work at
OL,13,Fpace to develop a strategy which could
OL,14,Fhelp make a meaningful difference to
OL,15,Fthose experiencing socio-economic
OL,16,Fdisadvantage in our society.
