OL,3,CPoverty strategy 'significant step
OL,4,Cforward' despite criticism, says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,F"I and my Executive colleagues have
OL,8,Fworked to develop a strategy which we
OL,9,Fwill make progress against and can and
OL,10,Fwill make a difference to people's
OL,11,Flives.
OL,13,F"This strategy is the culmination of
OL,14,Fconsiderable hard work, collaboration
OL,15,Fand co-design, and I want to thank all
OL,16,Fthose stakeholders, in particular the
OL,17,Fmembers of the anti-poverty co-design
OL,18,Fgroup, who have worked with my
OL,19,Fdepartment in providing their input.
