OL,3,CPoverty strategy 'significant step
OL,4,Cforward' despite criticism, says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,F"We often hear about the silo approach
OL,8,Fin government, but I know that
OL,9,Fministers and officials across the
OL,10,Fexecutive departments have worked
OL,11,Ftogether on the draft in a spirit of
OL,12,Fco-operation and collective ownership."
OL,14,FHe added that targets will come later
OL,15,Fwith an action plan following a
OL,16,Fconsultation process.
OL,18,FMark H Durkan from the official
OL,19,FOpposition at Stormont described the
OL,20,Fdocument as "underwhelming".
