OL,3,CPoverty strategy 'significant step
OL,4,Cforward' despite criticism, says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FHe contended it didn't just "call into
OL,8,Fquestion the Executive's ability to
OL,9,Ftackle poverty", but also their
OL,10,Fappetite and ambition to do so.
OL,12,FMr Lyons hit back, claiming Mr Durkan
OL,13,Fwas "wrong on every point that he
OL,14,Fmade".
OL,16,F"It has been 17 years that we have
OL,17,Fbeen waiting for this document, and
OL,18,Fafter 17 months in office, I have been
OL,19,Fable to bring this forward," he said.
