OL,7,FExisting budget pressures within the
OL,8,FExecutive have caused others to
OL,9,Fquestion how the action plan will be
OL,10,Fprioritised during future budget
OL,11,Fallocations.
OL,13,FMr Lyons said the plan outlines a
OL,14,F"realistic set of proposals" and hopes
OL,15,F"Ministers will find budget if
OL,16,Fadditional funding is needed."
